Then I went to POV with guild, and suddenly got pet 62. I decided that it was worth going to 62.<br>
Now I am 62, using water pet in groups, and he's a big killer. As I've not been lucky, I don't have lots of spells : I lost 13 rolls in the last 3 weeks, and I've got mantle and talisman in double (who cares ?...)<br>
<br>
I am not going to 63, I first want AA for SCM3, SCF3, Pet hold and some others.<br>
I'll go to 63 if I find a good spell (like summon bag of jewell ! this is really worth leveling)<br>
